msgstr "Rerank-model"

msgid ""
"Used only when rerank is enabled. English MiniLM is fast; bge-reranker-v2-m3 "
"is multilingual and downloads ~2.3 GB."
msgstr ""
"Alleen gebruikt wanneer rerank is ingeschakeld. De Engelse MiniLM is snel; "
"bge-reranker-v2-m3 is meertalig en downloadt ~2,3 GB."

