msgstr "Delegate (standaard)"

msgid "Direct — list all tools"
msgstr "Direct — alle tools weergeven"

msgid "Direct — discovery (find_tools)"
msgstr "Direct — discovery (find_tools)"

msgid "Python"
msgstr "Python"

msgid "Python venv path"
msgstr "Pad naar Python venv"

msgid ""
"If set, runs tools in that venv (bin/python or Scripts/python.exe). If "
"empty, run_venv_python_script uses this process's sys.executable (basic "
"stdlib); use a venv for numpy/pandas and Vision Helpers (paddleocr, "
"paddlepaddle)."
msgstr ""
"Indien ingesteld, worden tools uitgevoerd in die venv (bin/python of Scripts/"
"python.exe). Indien leeg, gebruikt run_venv_python_script de sys.executable "
"van dit proces (basis stdlib); gebruik een venv voor numpy/pandas en Vision "
"Helpers (paddleocr, paddlepaddle)."

